Maintainer: Guillaume Fabre <gfabre@maelstrom-research.org> 
Description: The goal of this package is to help the user through the processes 
    involving the Maelstrom Research guidelines. The user can: 
    a) Create an R environment where the user can place files in an organized structure. 
    b) Identify the location and content of files in user's environment. 
    c) Generate bookdown reports of study-specific variables (input). 
    e) Generate bookdown reports of study specific variables.       
